Call tree: downstream (default) or upstream (--reverse)

Usage: kodex calls [OPTIONS] <FQN>

Arguments:
  <FQN>  Symbol FQN (from search results)

Options:
      --depth <DEPTH>      [default: 3]
      --idx <IDX>          Path to kodex.idx (default: .scalex/kodex.idx, or `KODEX_IDX` env var)
  -r, --reverse            Walk upstream (callers) instead of downstream (callees)
      --exclude <EXCLUDE>
  -h, --help               Print help
